{"tid":2270989,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"政府尋求追加626億元撥款　兩司長辦公室佔最多","createTime":"2020-11-04T10:22:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-04T12:38:05.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a36b35c09ea7b2d8321bbadb2869a5079f399c58","tid":2270989,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T10:22:29.000Z","msg":"政府向立法會尋求626億元追加撥款，以應付2019至2020年度的額外開支。<br />\n<br />\n財經事務及庫務局副局長陳浩濂表示，追加撥款涉及28個開支總目，涉及不同政府部門，包括向防疫抗疫基金注資，以及公務員薪酬調整及逾時津貼等，又指所有超額開支已獲立法會相關委員會批准。<br />\n<br />\n追加撥款之中最大筆款項涉及政務司司長辦公室及財政司司長辦公室，開支約299億元，其次為大學教育資助委員會，涉及約216億元。另外警務處亦獲約30億元追加撥款，香港電台則獲約2000萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558366-20201104.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558366-20201104.htm&d=O3JFyT0uW1vU8ssvO3VcykV6NNh9RYlaag4wFuTDRgw%3D&h=d156927d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558366-20201104.htm&h=ac2dc006\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558366-20201104.htm</a>"},{"pid":"8a3bfbc1dffbb4dac49a7ba406e890c07d6803ed","tid":2270989,"uid":21470,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T10:24:15.000Z","msg":"夠晒票求鳩其走下程序姐<br />\n<br />\n通過 通過 通過 bom"},{"pid":"501615843fba3c080949590f3572f539838ecb80","tid":2270989,"uid":131181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T10:24:34.000Z","msg":"起咩要二百幾億"},{"pid":"083a7baeb60589ed6ca62cce6c886191eab3d50c","tid":2270989,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T10:41:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b234b9fa6d0707d2e059a3e414effea022497ef","tid":2270989,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"